comments: Collins (ATL) brings his hands toward Garland's (CLE) side and marginal contact occurs as Collins releases away to roll.
Young (ATL) engages and disengages with LeVert (CLE) as LeVert moves to re-screen along the perimeter.
Hunter (ATL) brings his right hand toward Garland's (CLE) left side and marginal contact occurs as Garland elevates away from the basket during the driving shot attempt.
Mobley (CLE) makes clean contact with the ball and knocks  it away from the lane prior to incidental arm contact occurring with Capela (ATL) and Collins (ATL).
LeVert (CLE) establishes himself in Hunter's (ATL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Young (ATL) brings his left hand outward toward Garland's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs with Garland's front as he continues his path to the basket.

Capela (ATL) brings his left hand toward Garland's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs with Garland's front as Garland's momentum continues to carry him forward after the release of the driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Young's (ATL) side after Young's gather. Mobley (CLE) legally contests Young's driving shot attempt.
LeVert (CLE) turns toward Capela (ATL) and engages with him momentarily as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Young (ATL) moves forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Garland's (CLE) side as they each pursue the rebound.
Garland (CLE) saves the ball back into play prior to landing out of bounds.
After the ball is saved back into play by Garland (CLE), the shot clock incorrectly does not re-set after Murray (ATL) gains control of the loose ball. The shot clock should have re-set to :24.
LeVert (CLE) legally contests Murray's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) engages and disengages with Mitchell (CLE) during the inbound.
Stevens (CLE) backs up slightly after establishing his screening position and he does not deliver illegal contact to Murray (ATL) as the screen is set during the inbound.
Mitchell (CLE) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps before elevating for the jump shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) establishes himself in Stevens' (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Based on available angles, Mitchell (CLE) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Murray (ATL) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Based on available angles, Mitchell (CLE) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds. Possession correctly remains with ATL.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in Garland's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he backs up slightly during the pick.
Collins (ATL) and Mitchell (CLE) engages and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Mobley (CLE) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Capela (ATL) during Capela's upward shooting motion.
Stevens (CLE) brings his right arm up and marginal contact occurs with Collins' (ATL) front as Collins attempts the controlled tip.
Murray (ATL) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Young (ATL) turns toward LeVert (CLE) with his hands brought outward slightly and marginal contact occurs with LeVert's front as LeVert crashes for the rebound.
LeVert (CLE) commits a take foul on Capela (ATL).
Garland (CLE) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Murray (ATL) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
